# Notes on the Document

## Records produced with the IA (as listed in Para 3 of the Affidavit)

1. **"Nomination as beneficiary"** — written in English in the Malayalam document; nature and date of the instrument not specified in the affidavit.
2. **Resolutions** taken at Alumoottil Tharavad Trust meetings (number not specified in the affidavit; previously stated as 5 in the 16/02/2026 counter-affidavit Para 9).
3. **Lease Deed dated 27/10/2025** between Alumoottil Tharavad Trust (lessor) and Sree Moolavasam Wellness & Leisure Retreats Pvt. Ltd. (lessee), registered at the *"Marad, Alappuzha Sub-Registrar's Office"* (മരട്, ആലപ്പുഴ സബ്ജ് രജിസ്റ്റാർ ഓഫീസ്).
4. **Statement of Account** for Federal Bank, Muttom Branch, Account No. 13100200004482 (in the name of Alumoottil Tharavad Trust), purportedly *"from 28/05/2005 to 15/05/2026"* — the year **2005** appears to be a typographical error in the original (the same paragraph confirms the account was opened on 28/05/2025).
5. **Original Minutes Book** of Alumoottil Tharavad Trust.

