## Significance for the case (brief note)

The defendants' filing of this IA on 18/05/2026 produces, on the court record, documents that the same Managing Trustee swore on 16/02/2026 were *"not available for production before the court"* (Para 13 of the 16/02/2026 affidavit). The contradictions across the two affidavits, the typographical error on the bank statement period (*2005* vs *2025*), the two-day discrepancy on the account-opening date (*26/05/2025* in 16/02/2026 affidavit vs *28/05/2025* here), and the assertion that Maradu SRO is in Alappuzha District (it is in Ernakulam District) are all features of the document as filed and may be relied upon as appropriate in subsequent proceedings.
